import React from 'react'
import { Grid, Image } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import "../../styles/Dashboard.css";
import ChangableStatistic from './ChangableStatistic';

const Section = () => (
  <Grid className="section" columns={3}>
    <Grid.Row>
    <Grid.Column>
        <ChangableStatistic name="star" color="green" degreeOfChange={3} text="Cookie Sold" />
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column>
      
      </Grid.Column>
      
    </Grid.Row>

    <Grid.Row>
      <Grid.Column>
      <ChangableStatistic name="thumbs down" color="red" degreeOfChange={1.5} text="Cookie Wasted" />
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column>
        <Image src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/wireframe/paragraph.png' />
      </Grid.Column>
    </Grid.Row>
  </Grid>
)

export default Section
